5000|$|Adolf Eichmann, {{one of the}} {{principal}} architects of the Holocaust, gave a figure of 6 <b>million</b> <b>Jewish</b> victims. This number was also used in July 1945 by Abba Kovner and then later by the first post-war trials of perpetrators. The Yad Vashem Museum writes that [...] "there is no precise figure for the number of Jews killed", but has been able to find documentation of more than three <b>million</b> names of <b>Jewish</b> victims killed.|$|R
