50|$|Schwarzbart and Zygielbojm played {{key roles}} in {{highlighting}} reports of Nazi atrocities against Jews in occupied Poland. In 1942 Schwarzbart {{held a press}} conference in London alleging that 1 <b>million</b> <b>Jewish</b> people had already been killed. The figures were reported in the media but were treated sceptically by both the British and by some other Polish politicians.|$|R
