5000|$|In 1992, {{his entire}} family decided to emigrate to the United States, {{settling}} in Suffolk County, Long Island, New York. It was only {{at this time}} that he discovered that the Holocaust had cost 6 <b>million</b> <b>Jewish</b> lives. As a result, Shapiro began writing in his native Ukrainian language, eventually writing several books, mostly memoirs about the war. His last book is entitled [...] "Зловещий марафон." ...|$|R
